SUMMARY:Bollywood & Bhangra Dance
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to move\, sweat\, and dance in this fitness-based dance class inspired by the vibrant rhythms of Bollywood and the powerful beats of Bhangra. Designed for all ages\, abilities\, and experience levels\, this class welcomes everyone — whether you’re stepping onto the dance floor for the first time or already love to dance. \n  \n  \n 
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/bollywood-bhangra-dance-2-2-4-2/2026-06-24/
LOCATION:Levy Park (Event Pavilion)\, TX
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/DSC0443_DxO.jpg
END:VEVENT
