SUMMARY:Children’s Bingo
DESCRIPTION:Bring the kiddos and join our Levy Park team for Children’s Bingo! This 30-minute program\, ideal for kids aged 4 to 12\, is a fun way for children to practice their letters and numbers while earning prizes. Levy Park provides Bingo cards\, markers\, and prizes. B-I-N-G-O!
