SUMMARY:Argentine Tango Series
DESCRIPTION:The world is dancing\, succumb to the mad rhythm of Argentine Tango! In this program\, you will be introduced to Tango fundamentals through rhythms and learn about musicality\, connection\, basic patterns\, and communication. You don’t need a partner or experience.
